    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"light\" people talk about feels like a lie. like, even if things get \"better,\" it's just more of the same cycle. life is just a series of chores and distractions until you eventually die anyway. why bother trying to find a way out of the dark when the darkness is actually the only thing that's real?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
